    "These limitations could be addressed in future studies by consideration of an expanded dataset to include more representative diverse and heterogeneous samples, investigating automated hyperparameter optimization techniques such as Bayesian optimization, and incorporating computationally efficient feature refinement methods to enable real-time deployment.",
    "Some limitations of the PolyNetDWTCADx framework include but are not limited to the relatively small size of the CKHK-22 dataset, which may not be representative of global variations in colorectal cancer cases.While manual annotations bring variability into the process and most of the time-dependent steps of segmenting the training data, this step is far more time-consuming in preparing a dataset.",
    "Although the overall computational resource requirement is only at a medium level when compared with Vision Transformers, it may still be above what can be afforded in resource-constrained environments [47] [48] [49] [50] [51] [52].",
    "In the light of these limitations, further work may consider expansion of the dataset with more representative samples, semi-supervised or unsupervised learning to reduce the burden of manual annotation, and further optimization of model architecture to reduce computational costs with minimal loss of accuracy.",
    "These will enhance the scalability and applicability of the framework in real-world diagnostic settings."
